    <div class="container" id="refund" style="text-align: left;">

        <center>
            <h1
                style="font-family:georgia,garamond,serif;font-size:16px; margin-top: 120px; text-align: center; font: normal normal 600 44px/51px Raleway; letter-spacing: 0px; color: #000000; opacity: 1;">
                CANCELLATION AND REFUND POLICY</h1>
        </center>

        <div style="font-family: SegoeUI; margin-top:50px; margin-bottom:50px;">
            <p>Travel plans can often change unexpectedly.We at AGIXURY believe in helping our customers in the event of such crisis. We encourage our
                customers to contact us in case of any issues faced,Team AGIXURY will be happy to help.<br><br>
                <strong style="font-weight: 700;">Booking effected by COVID-19 Cancellation & Refund Policy: </strong><br><em> Please note that in
                    case your booking has been imapacted by the ongoing coronavirus pandemic,the usual cancellation & refund policy is not applicable
                    and the following policy would apply instead:</em><br></p>

            <ul class="a">
                <li>In case you are unable to travel due to travel restrictions imposed by governments of your country of residence or your
                    destination country or in case the hotel is temporarily closed,you would be entitled to the following policies.</li>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        -AGIXURY will assist you with a free change in date to future date ,subject to the hotel's availability on the newly requested
                        date.</li>

                    <li> -All bookings will remain non-cancellable and non-refundable.Refunds will not be processed</li>
                </ul>


                <strong style="font-weight: 700;">Terms & Conditions of Cancellation & Refund Policy:</strong>
                <li> Customers have an option to cancel the booking within 7 days of purchase provided the cancellation date is at least 30 days
                    before the check-in date. Customers can choose the mode of refund here</li>
                <ul>
                    <li><b>a. </b>Customer's account as AGIXURY credits (can be used for future bookings) - Full refund</li>
                    <li><b>b.</b> Original mode of payment - 3.5% transaction charge would be deducted </li>
                </ul>
                <li> Customers can contact the Travel Concierge while at the destination if any inclusions mentioned in the package are not delivered.
                    If the customer fails to contact the Travel Concierge, he/she will not be considered for refund, if any.</li>
                <li>If the cancellation date does not meet the above criteria, customers are obliged to pay the full amount of the deal</li>
                <li>If the customer does not show up on the day of check-in he/she is obliged to pay charges equivalent to full stay. In case of
                    partial payments, the customer is supposed to pay the remaining amount before 30 days of arrival. In case of non payment booking
                    will be deemed cancelled without any refund</li>
                <li>One change in dates is permissible at no additional charge provided that the change is made at least 30 days before the original
                    arrival date and provided that the hotel has availability on the newly requested dates. The final decision regarding date changes
                    is at the sole discretion of the Hotel and the Hotel reserves the right to decline a change in dates should availability not exist
                    on newly requested dates.</li>
                <li>Scenarios where AGIXURY is not liable to pay any refund to the customer
                </li>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        <b> a. </b>if the refund request is made within 30 days before the check-in date
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <b> b.</b> No show on the day of check-in.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <b> c. </b>If the experience is not as per customer's expectation (Customer can get in touch with Travel Concierge regarding
                        the issue, we will try our best to improve your experience. However, AGIXURY is not liable make any refunds in this case)
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <b>d.</b> If the customer is unable to avail any inclusion due to unforeseen circumstances (weather conditions etc) AGIXURY is
                        not liable to make any refunds
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <b>e.</b> If there are any amendments/additions to the existing package (Transportation extra meals, additional facilities,
                        etc). the entire cost is to be borne by the customer. Any cancellations for this would be at the discretion of the service
                        provider, AGIXURY is not liable to make any refunds for the additions.
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <li style="padding-bottom: 30px;">
                    All refunds, subject to the terms and conditions would be processed within 14 days of cancellation. If a customer does not get the
                    refund within stipulated time, he/she can get in touch with our Travel Concierge
                </li>
            </ul>

            <h5 style="text-align: center; padding-bottom: 30px;"><strong>Have any queries?<a href="#" style="color:black; margin : 10px;">Contact
                        us</a></strong></h5>
